query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from answer AS a1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('10.10',
'alternative-proof',
'files',
'group-homomorphism',
'indicator',
'intel-graphics',
'irrational-numbers',
'keyboard-layout',
'live-usb',
'matrix-rank',
'maxima-minima',
'riemann-integration',
'update-manager')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 5
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10 group by t1.name;
